OL,3,CApologies and reveal agents:
OL,4,CStakeknife report key recommendations
OL,6,FIt said claims Stakeknife saved
OL,7,F'hundreds of lives' were unjustified.
OL,8,FAnd the agent carried out countless
OL,9,Fattacks and killings. It said lives
OL,10,Fsaved would have been in low figures.
OL,12,FIt found intelligence agencies'
OL,13,Fbilling of Stakeknife as the "goose
OL,14,Fthat laid the golden egg" was based in
OL,15,F"fairytales and fables" and the number
OL,16,Fof lives his actions may have saved
OL,17,Fwere in "low single figures" and it
OL,18,Fwas more than likely he cost more
OL,19,Flives.
