OL,3,CApologies and reveal agents:
OL,4,CStakeknife report key recommendations
OL,6,FThe report found those responsible for
OL,7,Fkillings were allowed to remain free
OL,8,Fto continue with their terrorist
OL,9,Factivities.
OL,11,FStakeknife was exposed as being
OL,12,FBelfast man Freddie Scappaticci, which
OL,13,Fhe always denied and Sinn Fein
OL,14,Fdescribed as 'British misinformation'.
OL,15,FThe report stops short of naming him
OL,16,Fbut calls on the government to allow
OL,17,Fthe identity of the agent to be
OL,18,Frevealed.
