OL,3,CApologies and reveal agents:
OL,4,CStakeknife report key recommendations
OL,6,FReport author and now PSNI Chief
OL,7,FConstable Jon Boutcher said the report
OL,8,Fwas a "key milestone" for legacy in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe Kenova interim report makes 10
OL,12,Frecommendations.
OL,14,F1. Establish, on a statutory basis and
OL,15,Fwith express statutory powers and
OL,16,Fduties, an independent framework and
OL,17,Fapparatus for investigating Northern
OL,18,FIreland legacy cases.
